---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Blog">
	<section class="blog-header">
		<h1>Blog</h1>
		<p>Thoughts, tutorials, and insights on web development and technology.</p>
	</section>

	<section class="blog-posts">
		<div class="posts-list">
			<article class="blog-post">
				<div class="post-header">
					<h2><a href="#">Getting Started with Astro</a></h2>
					<span class="post-date">July 11, 2024</span>
				</div>
				<p>Explore why Astro is the perfect framework for building fast, content-focused websites. Learn about its key features including islands architecture, zero JavaScript by default, and excellen[...]
				<div class="post-meta">
					<span class="category">Framework</span>
					<span class="reading-time">5 min read</span>
				</div>
			</article>

			<article class="blog-post">
				<div class="post-header">
					<h2><a href="#">Web Performance Tips</a></h2>
					<span class="post-date">July 10, 2024</span>
				</div>
				<p>Learn practical techniques to optimize your website's loading speed and user experience. We'll cover image optimization, code splitting, caching strategies, and more to make your site light[...]
				<div class="post-meta">
					<span class="category">Performance</span>
					<span class="reading-time">8 min read</span>
				</div>
			</article>

			<article class="blog-post">
				<div class="post-header">
					<h2><a href="#">Building with Components</a></h2>
					<span class="post-date">July 9, 2024</span>
				</div>
				<p>A deep dive into component-based architecture and why it matters for scalable projects. Understand the benefits of breaking your UI into reusable, maintainable components.</p>
				<div class="post-meta">
					<span class="category">Architecture</span>
					<span class="reading-time">6 min read</span>
				</div>
			</article>

			<article class="blog-post">
				<div class="post-header">
					<h2><a href="#">CSS Best Practices 2024</a></h2>
					<span class="post-date">July 8, 2024</span>
				</div>
				<p>Master modern CSS techniques including CSS Grid, Flexbox, CSS variables, and container queries. This comprehensive guide covers everything you need to know about styling in 2024.</p>
				<div class="post-meta">
					<span class="category">CSS</span>
					<span class="reading-time">10 min read</span>
				</div>
			</article>

			<article class="blog-post">
				<div class="post-header">
					<h2><a href="#">JavaScript Tips and Tricks</a></h2>
					<span class="post-date">July 7, 2024</span>
				</div>
				<p>Level up your JavaScript skills with lesser-known features and best practices. From async/await to modern array methods, discover powerful techniques to write cleaner code.</p>
				<div class="post-meta">
					<span class="category">JavaScript</span>
					<span class="reading-time">7 min read</span>
				</div>
			</article>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>

<style>
	.blog-header {
		text-align: center;
		padding: 2rem 1rem;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.blog-header h1 {
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
		color: var(--primary-color);
	}

	.blog-header p {
		font-size: 1.125rem;
		color: var(--text-muted);
		max-width: 600px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.blog-posts {
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 0 1rem;
	}

	.posts-list {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 2rem;
	}

	.blog-post {
		padding: 2rem;
		border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
		transition: all 0.2s;
	}

	.blog-post:hover {
		padding-left: 2.5rem;
	}

	.blog-post:last-child {
		border-bottom: none;
	}

	.post-header {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: space-between;
		align-items: baseline;
		gap: 1rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.blog-post h2 {
		margin: 0;
		font-size: 1.5rem;
	}

	.blog-post h2 a {
		color: var(--primary-color);
		text-decoration: none;
		transition: color 0.2s;
	}

	.blog-post h2 a:hover {
		color: var(--accent-color);
	}

	.post-date {
		color: var(--text-muted);
		font-size: 0.875rem;
		white-space: nowrap;
	}

	.blog-post p {
		color: var(--text-color);
		line-height: 1.6;
		margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
	}

	.post-meta {
		display: flex;
		gap: 1rem;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		font-size: 0.875rem;
	}

	.category,
	.reading-time {
		color: var(--text-muted);
	}

	.category {
		background-color: var(--bg-secondary);
		padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
		border-radius: 0.25rem;
	}
</style>
